00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:48.550
are really enthusiastic
about things like Tinder.

00:01:48.550 --> 00:01:50.740
And the reason why is because
online dating is never

00:01:50.740 --> 00:01:52.614
going to be able to do
much more for you than

00:01:52.614 --> 00:01:55.690
get you a broader pool
of potential partners

00:01:55.690 --> 00:01:58.540
and provide the opportunity
to get across a cup of coffee

00:01:58.540 --> 00:01:59.830
or a pint of beer.

00:01:59.830 --> 00:02:02.830
And that's the way you can
assess whether you're actually

00:02:02.830 --> 00:02:03.869
compatible with someone.

00:02:03.869 --> 00:02:05.410
LOGAN URY: So based
on your research,

00:02:05.410 --> 00:02:08.789
how would you design
the ideal dating app?

00:02:08.789 --> 00:02:10.259
