00:53:03.017 --> 00:53:05.350
of possible people out there
that you could go on a date

00:53:05.350 --> 00:53:07.150
with as soon as tonight?

00:53:07.150 --> 00:53:11.290
And here, I think I'm one of
the most optimistic people.

00:53:11.290 --> 00:53:13.180
And the reason why
I'm less concerned

00:53:13.180 --> 00:53:15.222
that having a singles bar
in your pocket is going

00:53:15.222 --> 00:53:16.638
is going to break
up your marriage

00:53:16.638 --> 00:53:18.700
or any long-term relationship
is because people

00:53:18.700 --> 00:53:21.472
who are happy in their
relationship aren't looking.

00:53:21.472 --> 00:53:23.680
So it doesn't matter that
there's a huge singles bar.

00:53:23.680 --> 00:53:27.490
I think the consequences
of having a big singles

00:53:27.490 --> 00:53:29.890
bar in your pocket
or in your purse

00:53:29.890 --> 00:53:32.650
are potentially
serious among people

00:53:32.650 --> 00:53:36.340
who are becoming dissatisfied
anyway, or at least starting

00:53:36.340 --> 00:53:38.560
to feel like, huh, I wonder
what else is out there?

00:53:38.560 --> 00:53:42.180
It lowers the friction
between the thought that says,

00:53:42.180 --> 00:53:44.804
huh, I wonder what's
out there, and now I'm

00:53:44.804 --> 00:53:45.970
actually pursuing something.

00:53:45.970 --> 00:53:48.400
Because going out
to a singles bar

00:53:48.400 --> 00:53:50.105
and starting to
flirt with someone,

00:53:50.105 --> 00:53:52.480
buying someone a drink, or
batting eyelashes, or whatever

00:53:52.480 --> 00:53:54.880
people do in singles'
bars, that is

00:53:54.880 --> 00:53:58.090
a pretty high bar for
saying, my marriage

00:53:58.090 --> 00:53:59.620
is really on the rocks.

00:53:59.620 --> 00:54:03.580
Downloading Tinder and swiping a
couple of times is a lower bar.

00:54:03.580 --> 00:54:06.460
So I actually think that is
probably the major consequence

00:54:06.460 --> 00:54:09.820
that will happen for the
prevalence of these things

00:54:09.820 --> 00:54:11.260
for existing relationships.

00:54:11.260 --> 00:54:13.990
I think the major consequences
for those people who

00:54:13.990 --> 00:54:17.350
are considering
alternatives already,

00:54:17.350 --> 00:54:21.254
they're more likely to take
the first step down that road.

